f=Product/ux/operational/skill/ux-skill-routing.md · h1:Skill Routing Map=`research request ─► research-repository (QUERY FIRST) ─verdict─► ANSWERED (cite, no study) \| STALE (re-validate) \| GAP \· │ \· GAP ─► study-design (protocol/method/sample/consent) ─► run \· │ raw data \· synthesis-discipline (claims + confidence + trace)` · h1:Skill Routing Map=Non-leader: law (the Evidence Gate evidence supply) routing decide WHICH skill WHEN. Handoffs out: spec (repo IDs PRD evidence; GAP-driven findings) loom (assumption checks, qualitative why) metric (behavioral magnitude metric's; co-cited) Client Success/future (read-only intake boundary) Behavioral Science/future (bias theory dependency, flagged inlined) anneal shipped miss traced stale/over-confident finding skill lesson). Precedence: query-first before any study; confidence flag rides claim; intake read-only support pipeline.